{"tid":2055274,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【向支那報仇？】匯豐收「虛擬銀行/電子錢包」手續費，高達2%！","createTime":"2020-06-07T23:26:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T08:05:50.000Z","uid":202464,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c58d8aea9420ade5bec1fa1fe87e41faf8dce45b","tid":2055274,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T23:26:31.000Z","msg":"1. 市場消息指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">滙豐銀行對部分虛擬銀行及電子錢包的eDDA服務收取高達2%手續費</span>，<br />\n<br />\n2. 惟其他銀行的收費普遍較低，有些僅收0.1%，甚至免費。<br />\n<br />\n3. <span style=\"color: red;\">有虛銀希望與滙豐就收費進行磋商，滙豐反應並不熱中</span>。<br />\n<br />\n4. 懷疑滙豐藉此減低虛銀使用該行eDDA服務的意欲，間接防止該行的存款流失。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n5. 金管局：「該局不會亦不宜介入商業協議。」<br />\n<br />\n6. 銀行公會：「屬商業決定，不會評論個別情況。」"},{"pid":"f9ac18a7ad2328c2a257934a467227ab5fb404e7","tid":2055274,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T23:28:30.000Z","msg":"英國佬出名陰陰濕濕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢頭向支共跪底，轉頭就向支那寶、we7pay&hellip;&hellip;呢類支那企業報仇"},{"pid":"b5dfa3e744a77e4adffcf1d0af98075ba4c07939","tid":2055274,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T23:31:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af9427942bf48ac298adcee246073ab3f2b2aef4","tid":2055274,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T23:34:29.000Z","msg":"撐咗國安法，當然係你班支種身上賺返筆。"},{"pid":"b90142ab2756e88b3b0d81a6def9fbe0e288065c","tid":2055274,"uid":119609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T23:35:41.000Z","msg":"危害國家安全？"},{"pid":"496f2eb930f97c5b6c1015b2d35dbb13e0063512","tid":2055274,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b90142ab2756e88b3b0d81a6def9fbe0e288065c","tid":2055274,"uid":119609,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-07T23:35:41.000Z","msg":"危害國家安全？"},"c